      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical) used with documented version control; FDA in-house code verified against published benchmarks. Required gradation 2 for Medium model risk.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2 employed with full version control and regression test suite. FDA in-house Python pre/post-processing scripts managed under Git with unit tests achieving >90% coverage. Achieved gradation 3 exceeds required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
