    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is bounded by the explicit COU restriction to ASTM F1717 compression-bending loading only; no extrapolation to other load cases is claimed. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) satisfied for all three QoIs across N=11 constructs and two independent laboratories. The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU at Medium assurance level.",
